Jerome Amerika was found guilty by the Western Cape High Court on Thursday for raping and killing his ex-girlfriend s 10-year-old sister.The 23-year-old was arrested in February after the child s body was found in a relative s house that stood adjacent to her parent&#8217;s Wendy House.This comes after three women have been murdered in separate attacks in Cape Town over the past few days.The incidents again highlight the country&#8217;s disturbingly high rate of gender violence in the country and marks 16 Days of Activism campaign.The state and defence concluded sentencing proceedings against Amerika on Thursday in the Western Cape High Court. State Prosecutor Maria Marshall has called for a life sentence to be imposed on Amerika.Amerika&#8217;s sentencing will start on Monday .&nbsp;-TNA Reporter